<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-20-0192 </DOCNO><TEXT>The dictionary contains approximately 5,000 entries in each of the fourlanguages covered (English, German, French and Russian). This dictionaryprovides a comprehensive collection of terms used in high-energy physics.The terms were compiled from specialized literature, including the mostrecent reports from research institutes and proceedings of conferences.The dictionary uses the approved lexicographical system of the otherdictionaries. To each entry is added the special field from which theterm derives and further information that may help in understanding thecorrect meaning of the term. The alphanumeric arrangement allows theuser to translate from any of the four languages into any of the otherlanguages included.</TEXT></DOC>